comments: Sabonis (IND) and Noel (NYK) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in McConnell's (IND) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Sabonis (IND) places his forearm on Randle's (NYK) front during his drive and affects his SQBR.
Rose (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in Turner's (IND) path and absorbs the contact.
Noel (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in McConnell's (IND) path and does not deliver contact.
Sabonis' (IND) hand briefly gets tangled up in Randle's (NYK) jersey and releases during the shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) grabs Noel's (NYK) jersey and moves into his body, which dislodges him.
Noel (NYK) makes contact with Sabonis (IND) arm at the start of his drive and affects his SQBR.
Holiday (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in Randle's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact.
Sabonis (IND) hands off the ball in Bullock's (NYK) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact with Noel's (NYK) arm during the rebound and affects his ability to gather the loose ball.
Sabonis (IND) moves in a direct path toward the basket and absorbs the contact initiated by Randle (NYK) during his driving shot attempt.
Holiday (IND) reaches across Barrett's (NYK) body as he attempts to commit a take foul and delivers contact on the perimeter.
Sumner (IND) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Sabonis (IND) briefly engages with Noel (NYK) and separates during the rebound.
Holiday (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in Ntilikina's (NYK) path and marginal contact occurs.
Sumner (IND) moves laterally into Ntilikina's (NYK) path and makes contact, which affects Ntilikina's SQBR.
Rose (NYK) moves laterally into McConnell's (IND) path in the backcourt and makes contact, which affects McConnell's SQBR. The contact occurs prior to McConnell's upward shooting motion.
